Wendel may sell its stake in
Stallergenes SA as the maker of allergy drugs is seeking a new
partner to help it market its Oralair hay-fever treatment, La
Tribune reported, without citign anyone.  Stallergenes wants a new partner by the end of the first
half of 2011, the newspaper said. 